  "title": "Logistics Officer | Manufacturing MNC | Incoterms",
  "description": "<p>Our client is <strong>European MNC in Machinery Manufacturing.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Procurement and Logistics Coordinator to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West Area.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and manage shipping, import, and export documentation (e.g., invoices, packing lists, delivery orders) in accordance with Incoterms 2020.</li><li>Coordinate the logistics and transportation of goods with internal teams and external forwarders to ensure timely and cost-efficient delivery.</li><li>Communicate with customers, suppliers, and logistics partners to monitor delivery schedules and ensure on-time performance.</li><li>Provide administrative support for procurement activities, including raising purchase orders, maintaining procurement records, and ensuring compliance with Gate 4 process requirements.</li><li>Assist in vendor qualification and approval processes, keeping the vendor master list in SAP and/or Business Central up to date.</li><li>Track and expedite orders, follow up with vendors, and address any delivery or quality issues promptly.</li><li>Ensure procurement and logistics activities adhere to company policies, client requirements, and ISO/BC standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Nitec in Logistics, Supply Chain, or Business Administration or related discipline.</li><li>Minimum of 2 years experience in logistics and procurement,</li><li>Understanding of Incoterms 2020</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Email Address: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</p>",
